title: Dystopian novel 1984 is a winner with Riae
description: Curvy Riae is a 5’2 model with a large number of colourful tattoos – which she shows off in many of her barely-there outfits. In one cheeky shot, she leans forward on her hands and knees in front of the washing machine She captioned the snap: “Things you can do at home: find the lost socks in the washing machine.” The model, who tells fans to be “proud of your weirdness” has a massive 3.1 million followers. And many were blown away by the saucy shot. One said: “I really hate doing that s***... but have to say you make it look fun!” While another joked: “And this is the reason why I can't open my phone on public.”
